%F A190917 a(n) = A110706(n) / 6 for n >= 1.
%F A190917 n*(n+1)*a(n) - (n+1)*(7*n-4)*a(n-1) - 8*(n-2)^2*a(n-2) = 0. - _R. J. Mathar_, Nov 01 2015 from A110706
